description: Hank, writer, impresario, photographer, record producer, knew Bob Wilber well -- not as a "Dixieland clarinetist."  In this interview, other notables pop up -- Marian McPartland and Margot Fonteyn, Eddie Condon, Bobby Hackett and Vic Dickenson, the World's Greatest Jazz Band, Teddy Wilson, Bobby Hackett, Soprano Summit, Bobby Henderson, Pug Horton, Summit Reunion, and more.  Recorded by Michael Steinman for JAZZ LIVES (http://www.jazzlives.wordpress.com) at Hank's office in downtown Manhattan, August 27, 2019.
